{"tid":1646243,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"快閃新地點！ 中共香港既辦公室！","createTime":"2019-10-11T08:18:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T09:20:38.000Z","uid":267864,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"66e4cbfb9dc41f234121eccba43cdd8bc5576a55","tid":1646243,"uid":267864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T08:18:23.000Z","msg":"<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">三大中共入侵香港的辦公室</span></strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中聯辦</span></span><br />\n香港物業非常多！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NDbQnjp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNDbQnjp.png&h=085fbb90&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n特別可以留意三大辦公室位置 <br />\n佢仲要用依啲物業黎炒樓，仲要可以免稅！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新華社</span></strong></span><br />\n一直大家都冇留意到佢，係中共既情報機構同埋宣傳、統戰部門<br />\n地址： 皇后大道東381號 （灣仔）<br />\n就係伊館對面！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中共外交駐港特派專員公署</span></strong><br />\n一樣係統戰部門！<br />\n半山堅尼地道42號  （金鐘上半山）<br />\n<br />\n就睇下，警方你要用幾多兵先守得到咁多個地方！<br />\n大家快閃又可以諗多幾個地方，睇下你死守到幾多個地方！"},{"pid":"7a7963f118db9ff419af397e38f72889a66788d7","tid":1646243,"uid":53592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T08:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60652c3b695668d14cc35be9ff5027624937a45c","tid":1646243,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T09:11:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1fbaaf387e86ee2eab2ad64909b69b5cf60dc07","tid":1646243,"uid":299255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T09:20:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"